// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0004 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c7aecad5-727b-51d0-b0e4-f59257298c21

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*")
